title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 8 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 8 2021
description:
The Defund the Police movement is the single dumbest idea in the 21st century. Journalist Nolan Peterson from on the ground in Kiev, Ukraine with an account of what's really going on. The hottest prime minister in the history of Democracy. Montana Senator Steve Daines on voting against overturning Biden's vaccine mandate for private businesses, the border disaster, and polls.
